letter.title: Open Letter
letter.content:
Company 751 / General Department of Technology / Ministry of Defense, a heroic unit of the people's armed forces, was established in 1975 on the basis of taking over the army factory of puppet regime, Saigon is a direct enterprise. serving the national defense and security and being the biggest technical guarantee base of the Army in the south.

The company is currently investing in many modern and advanced technology equipment; premises system over 600,000 m2, workshops over 150,000 m2; A contingent of well-trained managers in and out of the Army, a team of experienced engineers and workers ready to meet the requirements of our customers in business, cooperation and joint ventures. Links with all partners at home and abroad.
